open http://localhost:3000
```

### 8.2 生产环境部署

#### Docker 部署

```dockerfile
# Dockerfile
FROM node:18-alpine

WORKDIR /app

# 安装依赖
COPY package*.json ./
COPY dashboard/package*.json ./dashboard/
RUN npm install
RUN cd dashboard && npm install

# 构建项目
COPY . .
RUN npm run build
RUN cd dashboard && npm run build

# 暴露端口
EXPOSE 3000

# 启动服务
CMD ["npm", "start", "--", "--auto", "--enable-dashboard"]
```

